Highlighting search results:
:set hls	- enable
:nohls		- disable
%y			- yank all lines in file
%y+			- yank all lines in file to clipboard
D			- delete from cursor to the end of the current line
:m 10		- сдвинуть строчку на 10 строк вниз
:s/str1/str2/g - заменить str1 на str2 в текущей строке
%			- jump to matching bracket
C-w C-r		- swap 2 split windows
gg			- go to start of file
Cb			- change before

#	NERDTree
c + ww - toggle NERDTree/file in vim
